 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f6f4bcdda3907f9fd5e8cb68d2423ea4366211","tid":1842741,"uid":222665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"用緊8850，<br />\n諗住平平地買多部3310做副機"},{"pid":"17152454674f008b8e641e37fe59e7651f87ee0f","tid":1842741,"uid":222665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f298de3eb5ffd0549f79d2c8d98ed93d5c2612d2","tid":1842741,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"同時想穿入手機繩的人, 小弟未有發現可以穿入手機繩的地方, 很可能要好像Nokia 3210 般找一個合適的地方吧!<br />\n<br />\n冇手機繩咪好易跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"等8250啦，<br />\n可以穿手機繩"},{"pid":"33659bf00ab497128eeee218bd09678b0a9605f4","tid":1842741,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"聲控功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2979d53f05cf7607dea353a7bb465b3f002f98c","tid":1842741,"uid":18547,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n個樣型過今時今日d smartphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2299876809ab7ac09e969b78aaf5d4f51f700092","tid":1842741,"uid":222665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3404fb40272f7ba655155e655c7ef1ee5a376b1c","tid":1842741,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"當年由6150轉用3310<br />\n換咗個白色原廠殼幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"唔計Composer入歌仔 同可換殻<br />\n6150功能係齊過3310<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal